Question: Wine is pouring into a glass that stands in front of a wine bottle.

Reference Answer: True

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is wine pouring into a glass?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is wine pouring into a glass?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the glass standing in front of a wine bottle?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the glass standing in front of a wine bottle?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
